1.定位(position)和布局(Layout)

* position
* top/bottom/left/right
* float/clear
* flexbox
  * flex-direction
  * justify-content
  * align-items
  * ...

2.展示Display和可见(Visibility):

* display
* opacity
* visibility

3.盒子模型(Box Model) 顺序

* margin
* box-shadow
* border
* border-radius
* wdith/height
* padding

4.字体(Font) 文本(text)

5.background

* background-image/size/position/color

6.其他

* transform/transition/animation/overflow/white-space



### css编写顺序的思路

#### 1.1先确定盒子本身是如何布局

* position: absolute
* float:left/right
* display: flex

#### 1.2.盒子的特性和可见性

* display: block/inline-block/inline/none
* visibility/opacity

#### 1.3.盒子模型

* width/height
* box-sizing
* margin/border/padding/content
* box-shadow/text-shadow

#### 1.4.内部的文本文字

* font/text

#### 1.5.background

* background-image/size/position/color

#### 1.6.其他

* transform/transition/animation/overflow/white-space